News:

  History of user-visible changes.

  [-] version 0.1

      * recognition of the comment lines which start with `#' or `!'.
        note: this lines are ignored from the program.

      * use `GTRM_INPUT' environment variable.
      * use `GTRM_OUTPUT' environment variable.
      * add option `-o', `--option'.
      * add option `-i', `--input'.
      * add option `-a', `--again'.
      * add option `--usage'.
      * add option `--version'.
      * add option `-r', `--high-randomness'.

